{"tid":2512571,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"深夜限定心事台 (145)","createTime":"2021-05-01T22:30:30.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-01T22:50:04.000Z","uid":28236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"802ecf3606da5b887d8e6fc0ba7af1972f611bca","tid":2512571,"uid":28236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T22:30:30.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"large\"><strong>許願樹!</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n希望M47快啲到<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/yea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> (已實現)<br />\n屌你老濛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n牙女需要眼鏡仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n?!?!都想要眼鏡仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  (已實現)<br />\n王將<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n木星要發達<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n熊要熊啤啤同埋訓教唔好再俾人阻住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n村西透可以做返自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  (已實現)<br />\n正字GPA爆4同埋搵到女朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n腳腳繼續GPA爆4入UST<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  (已實現)<br />\n料快啲有男朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nWiedersehen識好多仔仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n夢要身體健康<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n春野可以同女神一齊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n柴子考好ielts搭火箭去木星<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n牙鹿搵到個正常既女朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n范統可以順利入大學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nCake要寧濫勿缺 搵到啱既人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n女生快高長大 學業進步 身體健康 等等<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n腦盧生日前岀pool<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  (已實現)<br />\n寞人想睇到世界末日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"small\">其實我諗我都係想身體健康<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n老規矩<br />\n有心事又好無聊又好都可以放低係到<br />\n如果無見到無覆到麻煩提一提我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果想有心事私下傾可以加我tg<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/lingdong\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Flingdong&d=Z1ElB6oaYTZYlgUQOIdQNm9Dn5prBKp8mj11ELPip4s%3D&h=4a77f0c5\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/lingdong</a><br />\n所有野絕對保密<br />\n不過會覆得都好慢<br />\n有可能會過一兩日先覆你<br />\n因為我應該都係回post優先同有自己野要做<br />\n只要你放低我就會覆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果太多人搵/我真係覆唔到可以搵木星<br />\n@threebridges"},{"pid":"b1f1ca39282b8a70abb8261725a45e868160add4","tid":2512571,"uid":28236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T22:31:02.000Z","msg":"唔記得加願望<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/annoyed.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"545ea1852f7d4ccfc9a2cef2a39f8b1534f1f5b0","tid":2512571,"uid":4000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T22:32:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3153e3e2f965f2bb912ca788e647517d649ceb58","tid":2512571,"uid":4000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b1f1ca39282b8a70abb8261725a45e868160add4","tid":2512571,"uid":28236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T22:31:02.000Z","msg":"唔記得加願望<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/annoyed.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T22:33:38.000Z","msg":"覺得係時候有D唔入嚟嘅人可以delete add新人<br />\n你點睇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b62b3660535c124378fec9aee30eaf1d06bee00c","tid":2512571,"uid":28236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0